comments: Brown (BOS) and Siakam (TOR) mutually engage and disengage with one another in the post.
Brown (BOS) places a hand on Siakam (TOR) as he is about to enter his shooting motion and immediately removes it.
Poeltl (TOR) and Porzingis (BOS) briefly lock arms as the two players pursue the rebound.
Achiuwa (TOR) grasps Porzingis's (BOS) jersey and immediately releases it during the rebound.
Siakam (TOR) jumps along Hoiiday's (BOS) path and marginal body contact occurs as Holiday releases his pass at the end of his drive.
Siakam (TOR) steps forward into Porzingis (BOS) and the body contact is marginal.  Porzingis then spins away from the contact and Siakam avoids initiating contact during his shooting motion.
Tatum (BOS) reaches in and as he retracts his arm, marginal contact occurs with Schroder's (TOR) left shoulder that does not affect his SQBR.
Holiday (BOS) and Poeltl (TOR) make incidental body contact with each other as they both jump for the loose ball.
Porzingis (BOS) establishes himself in Schroder's (TOR) path and does not deliver illegal contact.  Porzingis then briefly grasps Schroder's left arm as the two players engage for post position.
Schroder (TOR) leans forward and the body contact initiated with Porzingis (BOS) during his shot attempt in the post is marginal.
Achiuwa (TOR) establishes himself in Holiday's (BOS) path and marginal contact occurs to Holiday's side as he defends over the pick.
Achiuwa (TOR) establishes himself in Holiday's (BOS) path and absorbs the contact.
Horford (BOS) extends a hand into Barnes (TOR) during the drive to the basket, but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.

Holiday (BOS) initiates contact to Barnes's (TOR) arm and affects his SQBR on the perimeter.  The contact occurs before Barnes is in his upward shooting motion and is correctly deemed a non-shooting foul.
Holiday (BOS) and Schroder (TOR) mutually engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Brown (BOS) and Trent Jr. (TOR) briefly engage and disengage and Brown loses his footing on his own.
Barnes (TOR) avoids stepping out of bounds when he receives the ball.
Siakam (TOR) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
Barnes (TOR) commits a take foul on Holiday (BOS).
Horford (BOS) commits a take foul on Barnes (TOR).
Tatum (BOS) and Siakam (TOR) engage and Tatum releases from the contact without dislodging Siakam from his defensive position.
